Netflix Clone Frontend

This project is a Netflix-inspired frontend interface built using HTML and CSS. The homepage includes a responsive navigation bar with the Netflix logo and organized sections displaying show thumbnails. The design features a visually appealing layout with rows for all available shows, including a dedicated row for the Top 10 Trending Shows.

Features

Navigation Bar: Includes the Netflix logo and placeholder links for a user-friendly experience.

Show Thumbnails: Display of all available shows, creating a familiar Netflix browsing experience.

Top 10 Trending Shows: A separate row that highlights trending shows, making it easy to discover popular content.

Responsive Design: Optimized for various screen sizes to ensure accessibility on different devices.


This project provides a clean and minimalistic Netflix-like frontend using only HTML and CSS. Perfect for those interested in web design and frontend development.
